# ============================================================
# TRANSPORT CORE POLICY
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: policy
domain: transport
scope: transport.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines policy constraints for transport.

## policy_rules
Transport policy constrains:
- who may initiate or operate transport
- which routes/crossings are valid
- what transport detail may be disclosed
- when transport paths must be denied or escalated

## required_behavior
- route and operator scope must be explicit
- disclosure scope must be explicit
- denial behavior must be explicit
